---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const base = '/Jo-Ah-Kim-s-History-Trip';
---

<Layout title="Thailand Handoff" description="Details for the handoff in Bangkok, Thailand, including arrival card requirements and visa exemptions.">
  <main class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Thailand Handoff</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Closing the Vietnam week and meeting the family in Bangkok.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="handoff-content card">
      <div class="handoff-hero section">
        <h2 class="section-title">The Transition</h2>
        <p>On May 30, the historical journey through Vietnam concludes with a flight from <strong>Ho Chi Minh City (Tan Son Nhat)</strong> to <strong>Bangkok (Suvarnabhumi)</strong>. This marks the transition from the hosted history week to the family reunion with wife and child.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="practical-notes grid">
        <div class="note-card border-p">
          <h3>Thailand Digital Arrival Card</h3>
          <p>The <strong>Thailand Digital Arrival Card (TDAC)</strong> is currently mandatory for all foreign nationals. Details must be submitted on the official Thai Immigration portal within <strong>72 hours (3 days)</strong> before arrival.</p>
          <p class="accent-note"><em>Proceed with the official link below once within the 72-hour window.</em></p>
          <a href="https://tdac.immigration.go.th/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline small">Official TDAC Portal</a>
        </div>

        <div class="note-card border-p">
          <h3>Visa Exemption</h3>
          <p>Swiss and Liechtenstein passport holders are currently eligible for the <strong>Visa Exemption Scheme</strong>, allowing for a stay of up to <strong>60 days</strong> for tourism purposes without a visa.</p>
          <p class="muted-note"><em>Subject to current official conditions at the time of travel.</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="handoff-style section">
        <h3>Arrival in Bangkok</h3>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li><strong>Passport Validity:</strong> Ensure at least 6 months remaining.</li>
          <li><strong>Onward Ticket:</strong> Proof of return or onward travel may be requested.</li>
          <li><strong>Meeting Point:</strong> Coordination with family for airport pickup or hotel meeting.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .handoff-content {
    background-color: white;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .border-p {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  }

  .accent-note {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    display: block;
  }

  .muted-note {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .check-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .check-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .small {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
